Description:
FORGET EX-DISPLAYS, HOW ABOUT A REAL DISPLAY?
"On the exclusive cusp of Timbertop is your chance to secure a genuine display home."
Whether you are looking to move in or take advantage of the remarkable 10% rental return, this three bedroom property will leave you in awe.
The supremely-presented Dennis Family Homes-built property comes with all the added features you would expect to find in a modern day display home.
Only a brisk walk from Timbertop Boulevard, the property is ideal for an investor, down-sizer and still affordable for a first home-buyer.
Featuring:
- Three generous-sized bedroom, master with en-suite and walk-in robe;
- Two spacious living areas;
- Kitchen with butler's pantry;
- Double car garage with internal access;
- Alfresco overlooking the established backyard.
Call for an inspection.
